src="./images/fix.gif">
        <a href="https://bz.apache.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=61224">61224</a>: Make the <code>GlobalRequestProcessor</code> MBean
        attributes read-only. Patch provided by Alexis Hassler. (markt)
      </li>
    </ul>
